=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個THAAD應該講緊AN/TPY2?因為THAAD係個系統來，雷達只係部件</blockquote><br />\n係THAAD系統入面運作既AN/TPY-2 都係以terminal mode運作  主力針對高空目標   同PAVE PAWS比上黎FOV完全無得比 不過樂山一開戰一定比人炸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係日本用緊既AN/TPY2應該係用Forward Based Mode(FBM)運作 下面份野都有寫<br />\n<a href=\"http://lts-wiki.com/Publications/ATP%203_27x5.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flts-wiki.com%2FPublications%2FATP%25203_27x5.pdf&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=10c931d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://lts-wiki.com/Publications/ATP%203_27x5.pdf</a><br />\n GEM has improved algorithms for down-select tracks for AN/TPY-2 (FBM) system to forward a track to TDL-J/Link-16 network and Japan<br />\nand HN.<br />\n用黎做surveillance 個時有人計過可以係2,900~3,000公里睇到0.01m^2既object"},{"pid":"8367a4767beab45b92a5e1c90f61dab44bb6e5ef","tid":189530,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:50:22.000Z","msg":"美帝最缺既係錢<br />\n唔會打住啦<br />\n又未比人踩到上心口"},{"pid":"2aba637fa80957f0364468cdd36299b5741af406","tid":189530,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:55:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f386e694a3f662280c2049e388e26072601473f8","tid":189530,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:06:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國根本打就打, 唔需要理咩難民<br />\n因為佢之前打完阿富汗成班難民都係側邊國家同歐洲執手尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n難民 最主要係來自敘利亞<br />\n<br />\n伊拉克, 阿富汗比較小"}]}